hadiths[83]{hadithnumber,text}:
198,"Hazrat Abdullah Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri taraf se pahuncha do chaahe eik aayat hi ho, Bani-Israel ke waqiyat bayan karo is mein koi harj nahin, aur jo shakhs amadan mujh par jhoot boley wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' (Bukhari 3461) ."
199,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub aur Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs mujh se hadees bayan karey, wo janta ho ke ye jhoot hai to wo bhi jhooton ( hadees ghadney walon ( mein se eik hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
200,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah jiskey sath bhalai ka irada farmata hai to usey Deen ke mutalliq samajh bojh ata farma deta hai, main to sirf ( ilm ( taqseem karney wala hun jabkey (faham/samajh) Allah ata karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 71 w Muslim ."
201,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' insan bhi soney aur chaandi ki kanon ki tarah eik kaan hain, un mein se jo daure-jahiliyat mein achey they, wo Islam mein bhi achey hain b-sharte-ke wo (deen mein) samajh-boojh paida keren.'' rawahu Muslim w Bukhari ( 3493 , 3496 ( ."
202,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do qism ke logon par rashk karna jayez hai, eik wo aadmi jisey Allah ne maal ata kya, aur phir usko raahe-haq mein usey kharch karney ki tofiq ata farmaey, aur eik wo aadmi jisey Allah ne hikmat ata ki aur wo uskey mutabiq faisla karta hai aur usey ( dusron ko) sikhata hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 73 w Muslim ."
203,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab insan faut ho jata hai to teen kamon, sadqa jaariya, wo ilm jis se istifaada kya jaey aur nek aulad jo uskey liye dua karey, ke siwa uskey aamaal ka silsila toot jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
204,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi momin se duniya ki koi takleef door ki, to Allah us se qiyamat ke din ki koi takleef door farma dega, jis shakhs ne kisi tang-dast par aasani ki to Allah is par duniya w aakhirat mein aasani farmaeyga, jisney kisi musalman ki aeb-poshi ki to Allah uski duniya w aakhirat mein aeb poshi farmaeyga, Allah bandey ki madad farmata rehta hai jab tak banda apney bhai ki madad karta rehta hai, aur jis shakhs ne talabe-ilm ke liye koi safar kya to Allah us wajeh se uskey liye raahe-jannat aasan farma deta hai, aur jab kuch log Allah ke kisi ghar mein ikhattey ho kar Allah ki kitab ki tilawat kartey hain aur aapas mein padhtey padhatey hain to un par sakeenat nazil hoti hai, rehmat unhen dhanp leti hai, farishtey unhen gher letey hain aur Allah apney paas farishton mein unka tazkira farmata hai, aur jiskey amal ne usey peechey kar diya to uska nasab usey aagey nahin badha sakega .'' rawahu Muslim."
205,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat sab se pehley Shahid ka faisla sunaya jaeyga, usey pesh kya jaeyga, to Allah usey apni nematein yad karaaeyga aur wo unka aetraaf kerega, phir Allah farmaeyga : tu ney unke badley mein) shukr ke taur par) kya kya? wo arz kerega : maine teri khatir jihad kya yahan tak ke mujhey Shahid kar diya gaya, Allah farmaeyga : tune jhoot kaha, kyonkey tune daade-shujaat hasil karney ke liye jihad kya tha, pas wo keh diya gaya. phir uskey mutalliq hukm diya jaeyga to usey munh ke bal ghaseet kar jahannam mein dal diya jaeyga . doosra shakhs jisney ilm hasil kya, aur usey dusron ko sikhaya , aur Quran karim ki tilawat ki, usey bhi pesh kya jaeyga, to Allah usey apni nematein yad karaaeyga, wo unka aetraaf kerega Allah puchega ke tu ney unke badley mein kya kya? wo arz kerega : maine ilm seekha aur usey dusron ko sikhaya , aur main teri raza ki khatir Quran ki tilawat karta raha , Allah farmaeyga : tu ney jhoot kaha, albatta tu ney ilm isliye hasil kya tha ke tumhen aalim kaha jaey aur Quran padha taake tumhen qaari kaha jaey, wo keh diya gaya, phir uskey mutalliq hukm diya jaeyga to usey munh ke bal ghaseet kar jahannam mein dal diya jaeyga, aur teesra wo shakhs jisey Allah Taala ne maal w zar ki jumla iqsaam se khub nawaza hoga, usey pesh kya jaeyga, to Allah usey apni nematon yad karaaeyga , wo unhen pehchan lega, to Allah puchega : tune unke badley mein kya kya? wo arz kerega : maine un tamam mawaqe par jahan kharch karna tujhey pasand tha, kharch kya, Allah farmaeyga : tune jhoot kaha, tune to is liye kharch kya ke tujhey bada sakhi kaha jaey, pas wo keh diya gaya, phir uskey mutalliq hukm diya jaeyga to usey munh ke bal ghaseet kar jahannam mein dal diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
206,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ilm ko bandon ke seenon se nahin nikalega balke wo ulama ki roohen qabz karkey ilm ko utha lega , yahan tak ke jab wo kisi aalim ko baqi nahin rakhega to log johlaa ko raees bana lengey, jab un se masla puchha jaeyga to wo ilm ke baghair fatwa dengey, wo khud gumrah hongey aur dusron ko gumrah karengey.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 100 w Muslim ."
207,"Hazrat Shaqiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) her Jumerat logon ko waaz w nasihat kya kartey they, kisi aadmi ne un se kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! main chahta hun ke aap her roz hamen waaz w nasihat kya karen, unhoney farmaya : sun lo ! her roz waaz w nasihat karney se mujhey yehi Amr rukawat hai ke main tumhen uktaahat mein dalna napasand karta hun, main waaz w nasihat ke zariey tumhara wesay hi khayal rakhta hun jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is andeshey ke pesh nazar ke ham ukta na jaeyn, hamara khayal rakha kartey they.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 68 w Muslim ."
208,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) koi guftgu farmatey to aap eik jumley ko teen martaba dohraatey yahan tak ke usey samajh aur yad kar liya jaey, aur jab aap kisi qom ke paas tashrif latey aur unhen salam karney ka irada farmatey to teen martaba salam kartey .'' Bukhari 95) ."
209,"Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya : meri sawari halak ho gaee hai, aap mujhey sawari inayat farma den , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas to koi sawari nahin.'' eik aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main usey aisey aadmi ke mutalliq batata hun jo usey sawari dey dega . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khair w bhalai ki taraf raahnumai karney waley ko , us bhalai ko sar-anjaam deney waley ke barabar ajr w sawab milega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
210,"Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham din ke pehley pahar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke eik qom aap ke paas aai unke badan nangey they, unhoney ooni dhaari daar ya aam chadaren pehan rakhi thin aur wo talwaarein hamaayel kiye huey they. un mein se eik ziyada tar, balke sab ke sab Muzar qabeele ke they, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un par faaqe ke aasaar dekhey to gham ki wajeh se aap ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya, aap ghar tashrif ley gaey phir bahar aaye. aapney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney Azan di aur iqaamat kahi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhaai, phir khutba irshad farmaya : ''logo ! apney rab se dar jaao jisney tumhen nafs wahid se paida farmaya, aur usi se uska joda paida kya aur un dono ki nasal se bahut se mard aur aurten phela din, aur us Allah se daro jiskey naam par tum eik doosrey se sawal kartey ho aur rishte-daari (ke talluqaat kaatney) se daro, yaqin jano ke Allah tum par nigraan hai.'' aur Sura Hashr ki aayat tilawat farmaai : ''aey eman walo ! Allah se daro , aur chahiye ke her mutanaffas dekh ley ke wo kal ke liye kya kuch aagey bhejna hai, aur tum Allah se daro , be-shak Allah tumharey aamaal se ba-khabar hai.'' pas kisi ne Dinar sadqa kya, kisi ne dirham , kisi ne kapda , kisi ne gehun ka saa aur kisi ne eik saa khajuren sadqa kin, yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chahey khajoor ka tukda sadqa karo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : Ansar mein se eik aadmi eik thaili uthaey huey aaya qarib tha ke uska haath usey uthaney se aajiz aa jata, balke aajiz hi aa gaya, phir log musalsal aaney lagey, yahan tak ke maine anaj aur kapdon ke do dher dekhay, yahan tak ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak ko soney ki tarah damakta hua dekha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Islam mein koi achcha tariqa shuru kya to usey uska aur uskey baad is par amal karney walon ka sawab milta hai, aur unke sawab mein koi kami nahin ki jati, aur jis shakhs ne Islam mein koi bura tariqa shuru kya to usko uska aur uskey baad is par amal karney walon ka gunah milta hai aur unke gunah mein koi kami nahin ki jati.'' rawahu Muslim."
211,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko najaaiz qatl kya jata hai to uskey qatl ka kuch hissey Adam (Alaihissalam) ke pehley bete par hota hai, kyonkey usney qatl ka tariqa ejaad kya tha.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 3335 w Muslim. hadees Muawiya (6276). ham hadees Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) (la yazaalu min ummati) baab sawab hazal-umma) mein zikr karengey, insha Allah taala."
212,"Hazrat Kasir bin Qais bayan kartey hain, main abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath dimashq ki masjid mein betha hua tha ke eik aadmi unke paas aaya aur usney kaha : abu-Darda! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke shehar se eik hadees ki khatir tumharey paas aaya hun, mujhey pata chala hai ke aap usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( barahe-rast ( bayan kartey hain. main kisi aur kaam ke liye nahin aaya, unhoney bayan kya, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs talabe-ilm ke liye safar karta hai to Allah usey jannat ki raah par gaamzan kar deta hai, farishtey Talibe-ilm ki raza-mandi ke liye apney par bichhaatey hain, zamin w aasman ki her chiz aur pani ki gehraai mein machliyan Talibe-ilm ke liye maghfirat talab karti hain, beshak aalim ki abid par is tarah fazilat hai jis tarah chaudahwin raat ke chaand ko baqi sitaron par bartari hai, be-shak ulama anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ke waris hain. aur anbiya (Alaihimussalam) dirham w Dinar nahin chhod kar jatey balke wo to sirf ilm chhod kar jatey hain, pas jisney usey hasil kar liya usney wafir hissey hasil kar liya.'' Imam Tirmizi ne raawi ka naam Qais bin Kasir zikr kya hai. rawahu Ahmed (5 / 196, 22057) w Tirmizi ( 2672 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 3641 ( w ibne-Maja ( 223 ( w Darmi (1 / 99, 349 ( w ibne-Hibban (80) ."
213,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se do aadmiyon ka zikr kya gaya, un mein se eik abid aur doosra aalim hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aalam ki abid par is tarah fazilat hai jis tarah meri fazilat tumharey adna aadmi par hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beshak Allah, uskey farishtey, zamin w aasman ki makhluq yahan tak ke chewnti apney bil mein aur machliyan, logon ko khair w bhalai ki taalim deney waley ke liye duaaey-khair karti hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2685 ( ."
214,Darmi ne Mak-hool se mursal riwayat bayan ki hai. aur unhoney '' do aadmiyon '' ka zikr nahin kya aur unhon ( Mak-hool ( ne kaha : aalim ki abid par is tarah fazilat hai jis tarah meri fazilat tumharey adna aadmi par hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai! ''uskey bandon mein se sirf ulama hi Allah se dartey hain.'' aur phir mukammal hadees bayan ki. rawahu Darmi (1 / 88 padhi. 295) .
215,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be shak log tumharey tabey hain, kyonkey log Deen mein samajh bojh hasil karney ke liye zamin ke aas-paas se tumharey paas aaeyngey, pas jab wo tumharey paas ayen to unke sath khair w bhalai ke sath pesh aana.'' rawahu Tirmizi (2650) w ibne-Maja (249)."
216,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''danai ki baat, daana shakhs ki gumshuda chiz hai, pas wo usey jahan paaey to wahan wohi uska ziyada haqdaar hai.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur Ibrahim bin Fazal raawi hadees ke mamley mein zaeef. qarar diya gaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2687 ( w ibne-Maja (4169)."
217,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik faqeeh, shetan par, hazar ibadat guzaaron se ziyada sakht hota hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi (2671) w ibne-Maja (222)."
218,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''talab ilm her musalman par farz hai, kisi aisey shakhs ko, jo uski ahliyat na rakhta ho, padhaaney wala, khinzeeron ke galey mein heerey-jawahirat aur soney ke haar dalney waley ki tarah hai.'' ibne-Maja, jabkey Behaqi ne (Muslim) tak Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kya hai, aur unhoney farmaya : is hadees ka matn mashhoor hai jabkey sanad zaeef. hai, aur ye riwayat mutaaddid tareeq se marwi (bayan) hai, lekin wo sab zaeef. hain. (zaeef, rawahu ibne-Maja ( 224 ( w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 1543 ( ."
219,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do khaslatein kisi munafiq mein ikhatti nahin ho sakti , achey akhlaq aur Deen mein samajh bojh .'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2684 ( ."
220,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs talabe-ilm ke liye safar karta hai to wo wapis aaney tak Allah ki raah mein rehta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2647 ( w Darmi."
221,"Hazrat Sakhara Azdi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ilm hasil karta hai to ye uskey sabiqa gunahon ka kaffara bin jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi ne is hadees ki sanad ko zaeef qarar diya hai aur us riwayat mein Abu-Dawud raawi zaeef hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2648 ( w Darmi (1 / 139 padhi. 567 )."
222,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin khair ( ki baaten ( sun sun kar sair nahin hota yahan tak ke uski ghaayat w inteha jannat ho jati hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2686 ( ibne-Hibban ( 2385 ( w al-Hakim (4 / 130 ( ."
223,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs se ilm ki koi baat poochhii jaey, jisey wo janta ho, phir wo usey chupaey to roze-qiyamat usey aag ki lagaam dali jaeygi .'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 263 padhi. 7541 , 2 / 305 padhi. 8035 ( w Abu-Dawud ( 3658 ( w Tirmizi ( 2649 ( w ibne-Maja 261 ( ."
224,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne usey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ( 264 ( .
225,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ulamaa se munazra kerney, nadanon ko shubhon mein mubtala karney aur logon ki tawajjoh hasil karney ke liye ilm hasil karta hai to Allah usey jahannam mein dakhil farmaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2654 ( ."
226,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne usey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ( 253 ( .
227,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs aisa ilm , jiskey zariey Allah ki razamandi hasil ki jati hai, mehaz duniya ka maal w mataa hasil karney ke liye seekhta hai to wo roze-qiyamat jannat ki khushbu bhi nahin paeyga.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 338 padhi. 8439 ( w Abu-Dawud ( 3664 ( w ibne-Maja ( 252 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 89 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 85)."
228,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us shakhs ke chehrey ko tar-o-taza rakhey jisney meri hadees ko suna, usey yad kya, uski hifazat ki aur phir usey aagey bayan kya, kabhi-kabhi ehle ilm faqeeh nahin hotey , aur kabhi-kabhi faqeeh apney se ziyada faqeeh tak baat pahuncha deta hai, teen khaslatein aisi hain jinkey barey mein musalman ka dil khayanat nahin karta : amal khalis Allah ki raza ke liye ho, musalmanon ke liye khair-khahi ho, aur unki jamaat ke sath lagey rehna , kyonkey unki dawat unhen sab taraf se gher legi ( hifazat karegi ( .'' ( rawahu Shafai ( fi risala page 401 fiqra : 1102, page 423 ( w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 1737 ( w Tirmizi ( 2658 ( w Ahmed (1 / 436 ( ."
229,"Hazrat Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja aur Darmi ne Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, albatta Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood ne (ثلاث لا یغل علیھن) se aakhir tak zikr nahin kya. (rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 183 padhi. 21924 ( w Tirmizi ( 2656 ( w Abu-Dawud ( 3660 ( w ibne-Maja ( 230 ( w Darmi (1 / 75,  235 ( w ibne-Hibban 72, 73)."
230,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah us shakhs ke chehrey ko tar-o-taza rakhey jisney ham se koi aisi chiz suni , to usney jaisey usey suna tha wesay hi usey aagey pahuncha diya, kyonkey kabhi-kabhi jisey baat pahunchaai jati hai wo uski, us sunney waley ki nisbat ziyada hifazat karney wala hota hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2657 ( w ibne-Maja ( 232 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 74 . 76 ( ."
231,"Darmi ne usey abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Darmi (1 / 75, 236 ( ."
232,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mujh se hadees bayan kartey waqt ehtiyat kya karo aur sirf wohi hadees bayan karo jiskey barey main tumhen ilm ho (ke ye meri hadees hai), pas jisney jaan-boojhkar mujh par jhoot baandha to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2951 ( ."
233,"Hazrat ibne-Maja ne ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai lekin ibne-Maja ne ye alfaz : '' mujh se hadees bayan kartey waqt ehtiyat karo aur wohi hadees bayan karo jiskey barey main tumhen ilm ho.'' zikr nahin kiye. rawahu ibne-Maja (30, 33) w Tirmizi ( 2257 ( ."
234,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran ke barey main apni raey se kuch kahey to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' rawahu ( 2950 , 2951) . aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs Quran ke barey mein ilm ke baghair koi baat kahey to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.''"
235,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran ke barey main apni raey se kuch kahey aur agar wo durust bhi ho tab bhi usney ghalati ki .'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2952 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 3652 ( ."
236,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran ke barey mein ikhtilaf w jhagda karna kufr hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 276 padhi. 7835 , 2 / 503 padhi. 10546 ( w Abu-Dawud ( 4603 ( w ibne-Hibban (73) w al-Hakim (2 / 223)"
237,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuch logon ko Quran ke barey mein jhagda kartey huey paya to farmaya : ''tum se pehley log bhi isi wajeh se halak huey, unhoney Allah ki kitab ke baaz hisson ka baaz hisson se radd kya, halanke Allah ki kitab to is liye nazil hui ke wo eik doosrey ki tasdeeq karta hai, pas tum Quran ke baaz hissey se baaz ki takzeeb na karo, us se jo tum jaan lo to usey bayan karo, aur jis ka tumhen pata na chaley usey uskey janney waley ke supurd kar do .'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 175  67419 ( w ibne-Maja (85) ."
238,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran saat qiraaton mein nazil kya gaya, is mein se her aayat ka zahir aur baatin hai, aur her satah ka mafhoom samajhney ke liye munasib istedaad ki zarurat hai.'' , ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah (1 / 263 baad padhi. 122 ( w Tabri fi tafseer (1 / 10 , 11) w ibne-Hibban ( 1781 ( w abi-Yaala fi masnada (9 / 81  5149 ( ."
239,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ilm teen hain : aayat mahakma ya sunnate-saabita ya fariza Aadila (her wo farz jiski farziyat par musalmanon ka ijmaa hai) aur jo uskey siwa ho wo afzal hai.'' (rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 2775 ( w ibne-Maja ( 54 ( fi talkhees (4 / 332)"
240,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ameer ya jisey wo ijazat dey wohi khitab karney ka majaz hai ya phir mutakabbir shakhs waaz karta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 3665 ( ."
241,"Darmi ne Amr bin Shuaib an abi an jadda ki sanad se riwayat bayan ki hai, is mein (mukhtaal) ''mutakabbir'' ke bajaey ( مراء ( '' ریاکار '' ka lafz hai. rawahu Darmi ( 2 / 319 padhi. 2782 ( ."
242,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne ilm ke baghair fatwa diya to uska gunah usey fatwa deney waley par hai, aur jis shakhs ne apney ( musalman ( bhai ko kisi mamley mein mashwara diya halanke wo janta hai ke bhalai w behtari uskey ilawa kisi dusri surat mein hai, to usney us se khayanat ki.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 3657 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 126 ( w ibne-Maja ( 53 ( ."
243,Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghalati mein dalney waley sawaalon se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 3656 ( .
244,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ilme-meeras aur Quran ki taalim hasil karo aur logon ko sikhao, kyonkey an-qareeb meri rooh qabz kar li jaeygi : ''rawahu Tirmizi ( 2091 ( w ibne-Maja ( 2719 ( ."
245,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, to aapney aasman ki taraf nazar utha kar farmaya : ''ye wo waqt hai jis mein logon se ilm salb kar liya jaeyga yahan tak ke wo us se kisi chiz par bhi qudrat nahin rakhengey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2653 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 99 ( ."
246,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke an-qareeb log talabe-ilm mein oonton par safar karengey, lekin wo aalim Madina se ziyada aalim kisi ko nahin paeyngey. aur unki Jaame mein hai ke ibne-Uena (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is se murad Malik bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) hain. unhi ke tarah abdur-Razzaaq se marwi (bayan) hai, Is-haq bin Musa ne bayan kya, maine ibne-Uena se suna, to unhoney kaha : is se murad Umri Zahid hai aur unka naam Abdul-Azeez bin Abdullah hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2670 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 91 padhi. 307 ( ."
247,Hazrat raawi hadees abu-Alqama bayan kartey hain ke meri maloomat ke mutabiq Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfoo riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall is ummat ke liye her so saal ke aakhir par kisi aisey shakhs ko bhejega jo uskey liye uskey Deen ki tajdeed kerega.'' ( rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 4291 ( w al-Hakim fil-mustadrak (4 / 522 ( .
248,"Hazrat Ibrahim bin Abdur-Rehman Azra (Raziallahu anhu) (mursal riwayat) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is ilm ko baad mein aaney waley her tabqe ke sahibe-taqwa log hasil karengey, wo us ( ilm ( se ghulu karney walon ki tehreef , jhootey logon ki jaalsaazi aur johlaa ki taaweel ki nafi karengey.'' Behaqi ne al-mudkhal mein mursal riwayat kya hai, ham Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ( فانما شفاء العی السوال) ko ( باب التیمم) mein inshaAllah bayan karengey. rawahu al-Behaqi ( 10 / 209 ( ."
249,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko ehyaae-Islam ke liye ilm hasil kartey huey maut aa jaey to jannat mein uskey aur Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ke beech sirf (nabuwat ka (eik darja hoga.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 100 padhi. 360 ( ."
250,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bani-Israel ke do aadmiyon ka tazkira kya gaya, un mein se eik aalim tha, wo farz Namaz padh kar beth jata aur logon ko khair ( ilm ( ki taalim deta , jabkey doosra shakhs din ko roza rakhta aur raat ko qiyam karta tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke un dono mein kon afzal hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us aalim ki, jo farz Namaz padh kar beth jata hai aur logon ko khair ki taalim deta hai, is par abid, jo din ko roza rakhta hai aur raat ko qiyam karta hai, is tarah fazilat hai, jis tarah meri tumharey adnaa par fazilat hai.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 98 padhi. 347 ( ."
251,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''deen ka faqeeh shakhs kya hi achcha hai agar uski taraf ruju kya jaey to wo faeyda pahunchata hai, aur agar us se be-niyazi barti jaey to wo bhi apney aapko be-niyaz kar leta hai.'' (rawahu rizeen w ibne-Asaakir fi taareekh dimashq ( 48 / 203 ( ."
252,"Hazrat Ikrima se riwayat hai ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : '' her Juma ( saat din ( mein logon se eik martaba waaz karo, agar tum (us sey) inkar kartey ho to phir ( hafta mein) do martaba , agar ziyada kartey ho to phir teen martaba , logon ko is Quran se uktaa na do, main tumhen na paaun ke tum logon ke paas aao aur wo apni guftgu mein masroof hon aur tum unki baat kaat karkey unhen waaz karna shuru kar do, is tarah tum unhen uktaa dogey, balke tum ( wahan ja ( kar khamoshi ikhtiyar karo, jab wo tumhen kahin to unhen waaz karo, dar-aan-haaleke wo uski khahish rakhtey hon aur sajey huey aur bhari-bharkam kalam mein dua karney se ijtinab karo, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba ko dekha ke wo aisey nahin kya kartey they. Bukhari 6337 ( ."
253,"Hazrat Wasila bin Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ilm talash karey aur usey pa ley to uskey liye do ajr hain, aur agar usey na pa sakey to uskey liye eik ajr hai.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 97  342 ( ."
254,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin ko apni maut ke baad apney maal w hasanaat mein jinka sawab pahunchta rehta hai, un mein se eik ilm hai jo usney sikhaya aur usey nashr kya, (doosra) nek aulad jo usney chhodi, ya Quran Majeed jo usney kisi ko Atiya kya, ya masjid hai jo usney banai ya musafir khana hai jo usney banaya, ya nehar hai jo usney jari ki ya wo sadqa hai jo usney apni sehat w hayaat mein apney maal se kya, pas ye wo aamaal hain jinka sawab uski maut ke baad bhi usey pahunchta rehta hai.'' (rawahu ibne-Maja ( 242 ( w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 3448 ( w ibn Khuzaima ( 2490 ( ."
255,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah azz-w-jall ne meri taraf wahi farmaai ke jo shakhs talabe-ilm mein koi safar karta hai to main uskey liye raahe-jannat aasan kar deta hun, aur main jiski dono aankhen salb kar leta hun to main uskey badley usey jannat ata kar deta hun, ilm mein ziyadati, ibadat mein ziyadat se behtar hai, aur Deen ki asal taqwa hai.'' ( sanda mauzu ( , ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 5751 ( ."
256,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, raat ki eik ghadi ki dars w tadrees raat bhar ibadat karney se behtar hai. rawahu Darmi (1 / 149 padhi. 620 ( ."
257,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjide-nabawi mein do halqon ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''dono khair w bhalai par hain, lekin un main eik doosrey se afzal hai, rahey wo log jo Allah se dua kar rahey hain aur uskey mushtaaq hain, pas agar wo chahey to unhen ata farmaai aur agar chahey to ata na farmaey, aur rahey wo log jo fiqh ya ilm seekh rahey hain aur jahilon ko taalim dey rahey hain, to wo behtar hain, aur mujhey to muallim bana kar bheja gaya hai.'' phir aap us halqey mein beth gaey. rawahu Darmi (1 / 99 , 100 padhi. 355 ( ."
258,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah se puchha gaya ke ilm ki wo kya had hai jahan pahunch kar insan faqeeh bin jata hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Deen ke mamlon ke mutalliq chaalis ahadis yad kin aur unhen aagey ummat tak pahunchaya to Allah usey faqeeh ki haisiyat se uthaeyga aur roze-qiyamat mein uskey haq mein shafaat karunga aur gawahi dunga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 1726 ( ."
259,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho sab se bada sakhi kon hai? '' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala sab se bada sakhi hai, phir aulade-Adam mein sab se bada sakhi main hun, aur merey baad wo shakhs sakhi hai jisney ilm hasil kya aur usey farogh diya, roze-qiyamat wo us haisiyat se aaeyga ke wo akela hi ameer hoga.'' ya farmaya : ''akela hi eik ummat hoga.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 1767 ( ."
260,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do qism ke bhookey kabhi sair nahin hotey, ilm ka bhooka shakhs kabhi ilm se sair nahin hota aur duniya ka laalchi kabhi duniya se sair nahin hota.'' Behaqi ne ye teeno ahadis Shobil-emaan mein bayan ki hain. aur Imam Ahmed ne abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke barey mein farmaya : is hadees ka matn to logon mein mashhoor hai, lekin uski asnaad sahih nahin. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 10279 , 9798 , 50) w ibn Adi fil-kamil ( 6 / 2298 ( w ibn jauzi w al-Hakim (1 / 92) w abi Khaisma fil-ilm ( 141 ( ."
261,"Hazrat Aun (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : '' do bhookey log sair nahin hotey sahabe-ilm aur sahibe-duniya, aur ye dono barabar bhi nahin ho saktey, raha sahibe-ilm to wo Rehman ki razamandi mein badhta chala jata hai, aur raha sahibe-duniya to wo sarkashi mein badhta chala jata hai. phir Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''haan bila-shuba insan sarkash ho jata hai, jab wo apney aap ko be-niyaz samajhta hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney doosrey ke liye ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''baat sirf ye hai ke Allah ke bandon mein se ulama hi us se dartey hain.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 96,  339 ( ."
262,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se kuch log Deen mein tafaqqoh hasil karney ka daawa karengey, wo Quran padhengey, wo kahengey : ham ameeron ke paas ja kar un se unki duniya se kuch hasil kartey hain, aur ham apney Deen ko un se bacha kar rakhtey hain halanke aisey nahin ho sakta. jaisey sakht kaantey daar jangli darkht se sirf kaantey hi chuney ja saktey hain, isi tarah un (ameeron) ke qurb se siwaye.'' Muhammad bin Sabaah ne kaha : goya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye kehna chahtey hain ke '' unke paas janey se gunah hasil hoga .'' rawahu ibne-Maja ( 255 ( ."
263,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : agar ehale-ilm, ilm ki hifazat kartey aur usey uskey ehle logon tak pahunchatey to wo uskey zariey apney zamaney ke logon par sayaadat w hukmrani kartey, lekin unhoney duniya daaron ke liye makhsus kar diya, taake wo uskey zariey unki duniya se kuch hasil kar lein, to is tarah wo unke samney be aabroo hogaye , maine tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''jo shakhs apney ghamon ko samet kar faqat apni (aakhirat ko) eik gham bana leta hai to Allah uskey duniya ke ghamon se uskey liye kafi ho jata hai, aur jis shakhs ko duniya ke gham w fikr muntashir rakhen to phir Allah ko uski koi parwah nahin ke wo kis wadi mein halak hota hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ( 257 ( ."
264,"Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qol : (من جعل الھموم) se aakhir tak riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 1888 ( w al-Hakim fil-mustadrak (4 / 327 , 329 ( ."
265,"Hazrat Aamash (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bhool jana ilm ke liye aafat hai, aur jo ilm ki ahliyat nahin rakhtey un se usey bayan karna usey zaya karna hai.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 150 padhi. 630 ( ."
266,"Hazrat Sufiyan Sory (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : ehle-ilm kon hain? unhoney kaha : jo apney ilm ke mutabiq amal kartey hain, phir puchha : kon si chiz ulama ke dilon se ilm nikal deti hai? unhoney kaha : ( duniya ka ( lalach. rawahu Darmi (1 / 144  590 ( ."
267,"Hazrat Ahwas bin Hakim apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : kisi aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shar ke barey mein puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mujh se shar ke barey mein mat puchho. mujh se khair ke barey mein poochho.'' aapney teen martaba aisey farmaya : phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! sab se bada shar Ulamaaye-soo hain, aur sab se badi khair Ulamaaye khair hain.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 104, 374 ( ."
268,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : '' roze-qiyamat Allah ke yahan sab se bura maqam us aalim ka hoga jo apney ilm se faeyda hasil nahin karta.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 82, 267)."
269,"Hazrat Ziyad bin Hudair (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se puchha ke tum jantey ho kon si chiz Islam ki izzat mein kami karti hai? maine kaha : nahin, unhoney farmaya : aalim ki laghzish, munafiq ka Quran ke sath Jidal karna aur gumrah hukmranon ka faisley karna.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 71, 220 ( ."
270,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : ilm ki do iqsaam hain, eik ilm dil mein hai, wo ilm nafa mand hai, aur eik ilm zaban par hai, wo Allah azz-w-jall ki ibne-Adam ke khilaf hujjat hogi. rawahu Darmi (1 / 102, 370) ."
271,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( ilm ke) do zuroof yad kiye , un mein se eik maine tumharey darmiyan nashr kar diya, rahi dusri qism to agar main usey nashr kar dun to mera gala kaat diya jaey. (Bukhari 120 ( ."
272,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : logo ! jis shakhs ko kisi chiz ka ilm ho to wo uskey mutalliq baat karey, aur jisey ilm na ho to wo kahey : Allah behtar janta hai. kyonkey jis chiz ka tujhey ilm na ho uskey mutalliq tumhara ye kehna ke Allah behtar janta hai, ye bhi ilm ki baat hai. Allah Taala ne apney Nabi se farmaya : ''keh dijiye, main is par tum se koi ajr nahin maangta aur main takalluf karney walon mein se bhi nahin hun.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 4809 w Muslim ."
273,"Hazrat ibne-Sereen (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : be-shak ye ilme-deen hai, pas tum dekho ke tum apna Deen kis se hasil kartey ho. rawahu Muslim ."
274,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aey Quran padhnewalon ki jamaat ! sidhi raah par Sabit qadam raho, is liye ke tum sabse aagey ho, aur agar tum daain baaeyn chaley gaey to tum bahut door gumrahi mein chaley jaaogey. (Bukhari 7282 ( ."
275,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (ghamnak gaddhey) se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! ghamnak gaddhey se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jahannam main eik wadi hai, jis se jahannam (ki dusri waadiyan) her roz chaar so martaba panah maangti hain.'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! is mein kon dakhil hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney aamaal ke zariey riyaakaari karney waley qurra.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2383 ( w ibne-Maja (256). isi tarah ibne-Maja ne riwayat kya hai, aur unhoney is mein ye izafa kya hai : ''Allah taala ke nazdik sab se naa-pasandida qurra wo hain jo ameeron ke paas jatey hain.'' maharibi ne kaha is se zalim ameer murad hain."
276,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qarib hai ke logon par eik aisa door aaye jab Islam ka sirf naam aur Quran ka sirf rasmul-khat baqi reh jaeyga, unki masaajid abad hongi lekin wo hidayat se khaali hongi, unke ulamaa aasman tuley bad-tareen log hongey, unke paas se fitna zahir hoga aur unhi mein lot jaeyga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan (1908) ."
277,"Hazrat Ziyad bin Labid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi ( khofnak ( chiz ka zikr kya to farmaya : ''ye ilm ke rukhsat ho janey ke waqt hogi .'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! ilm kaisey rukhsat ho jaeyga, jabkey ham Quran padhtey hain, aur ham usey apni aulad ko padha rahey hain, aur hamari aulad apni aulad ko padhaeygi aur ye silsila qiyamat tak jari rahega . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ziyad! teri maa tumhen gum paey, main to tumhen Madina ka bada faqeeh shakhs samajhta tha, kya ye Yahud w nasara Torah w Injeel nahin padhtey, lekin wo unke mutabiq amal nahin kartey.'' Ahmed, ibne-Maja, aur Tirmizi ne bhi unhi se isi tarah riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed (4 / 160, 17612 ( w ibne-Maja ( 4048 ( w Tirmizi ( 2653 ( ."
278,"aur Darmi ne bhi abu-Umama se isi tarah riwayat kya hai. rawahu Darmi (1 / 77, 78, 246 ( ."
279,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''ilm seekho aur usey dusron ko sikhao, faraaiz (ilme-meeras) seekho aur usey logon ko sikhao, Quran seekho aur usey logon ko sikhao, kyonkey meri rooh qabz kar li jaeygi, aur) merey baad) ilm bhi utha liya jaeyga, fitney zahir ho jaeyngey, yahan tak ke do aadmi kisi farizey mein ikhtilaf karengey lekin wo apney darmiyan faisla karney wala koi nahin paeyngey .'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 72, 73, 227 ( w Dar-Qutni (4 / 82 ( w Tirmizi ( 2091 ( ."
280,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ilm se faeyda na uthaya jaey wo us khazaney ki tarah hai jis mein se Allah ki raah mein kharch na kya jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 499 padhi. 10481 ( w Darmi (1 / 138 padhi. 562 ( ."
